data.description: Looking for a place to call home? This charming two-story home is now on the market! Inside, you'll find a perfectly flowing open layout cleverly designed to encourage conversation, connection, and effortless movement between the living, dining, & kitchen. The space is illuminated by an abundance of natural light pouring in, creating an inviting atmosphere. Cooking is a delight in this beautiful kitchen boasting ample wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and a large island w/a breakfast bar. Take advantage of the cozy loft, an ideal spot for an additional lounging area. All three bedrooms ensure a quiet and personal sanctuary. Finally, you'll enjoy sipping your favorite morning cup of coffee in this serene backyard. Visit before it's gone!
